---
/**
 * How It Works — three steps showing the voice-to-PDF flow.
 *
 * The argument: this isn't a digitised paper form. It's a different way of
 * working — speak the inspection, AI structures it, signed PDF generated on
 * the device before you leave the site.
 *
 * Numbered steps with clear visual hierarchy. No icons-as-decoration; the
 * numbers ARE the visual. Restraint reads as confidence.
 */
---

<section class="border-b border-brand-100 bg-brand-50">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-20 sm:py-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center">
      <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-brand-700">
        How it works
      </p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-brand-900 sm:text-4xl">
        From site visit to signed PDF, without leaving the playground.
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-slate-700">
        Three steps. No typing. No syncing back at the office.
      </p>
    </div>

    <ol class="mx-auto mt-16 grid max-w-5xl gap-10 sm:grid-cols-3 sm:gap-8">
      <li class="relative">
        <div class="mb-5 inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-brand-700 text-xl font-bold text-white">
          1
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-brand-900">
          Walk the site, dictate findings
        </h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-base text-slate-700">
          Open the asset, hold the record button, speak naturally. "Cracked
          weld on the swing frame, north-east corner, photo attached." The
          app captures voice and photos straight to the asset record.
        </p>
      </li>

      <li class="relative">
        <div class="mb-5 inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-brand-700 text-xl font-bold text-white">
          2
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-brand-900">
          AI extracts the defects
        </h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-base text-slate-700">
          Your dictation is transcribed and structured into discrete defect
          entries — risk rating, location, recommended action, photo evidence
          — using the same vocabulary your reports already use.
        </p>
      </li>

      <li class="relative">
        <div class="mb-5 inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-brand-700 text-xl font-bold text-white">
          3
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-brand-900">
          PDF generated on the device
        </h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-base text-slate-700">
          A polished, branded, BS EN 1176-aligned PDF report is produced on
          your phone or tablet before you leave the site. Email it to the
          client from the car park. Done.
        </p>
      </li>
    </ol>
  </div>
</section>
